rawContent:
under
the umber
canopy
of autumn
each leaf
offers the last
of it's beauty
then eventually
deserts it's tree
a suicidal cycle
yet always
reborn
in the spring
#vss365 #poetry #poet #poem #SundayMorning #sundayvibes
